reviewText: Love this show, subtitles are good. Wish they would dub this!
nice lovely family safe anime about friendship and fun at a overseas magical school.with crazy student inventions and an angry teddy bear.

I watched this series online with fansubs awhile ago and decided to show my support and pay for the real deal. I am a little sad there is not a dubbed version only for the fact I can't put this on in the background while doing other things because I need to be able to read the subtitles to know what is happening. Japanese language is much better in most anime than the Englsih dub, but it requires undivided attention.
I purchased this in February. It's perfect. It has all 26 episodes with English subtitles. It's a cute and funny series. Great gift!!
